Class ModifyPartController

  • java.lang.Object
    • controller.ModifyPartController
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javafx.fxml.Initializable
    public class ModifyPartController
extends java.lang.Object
implements javafx.fxml.Initializable
    Modify parts screen controller: Allows user to modify selected part and select in house or outsourced Alerts if invalid data is entered or if text fields are left blank
